ABOUT THE ARTIST: WHOMADEWHO

Made up of Tomas Høffding, Tomas Barfod, and Jeppe Kjellberg, this trio has electrified audiences all over the globe with their live shows. Their music blends electronic, rock, and jazz elements, creating a sound that's both distinctive and addictive. Always pushing their limits, they've delved deeper into electronic music, delivering unforgettable performances.
